  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "My husband got a job-- not-- not-- not necessarily a job that he would have liked because there was no industry in Luck, but a job that he could work.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "My father got a job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "My sisters got jobs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So for us-- for us, it was, at that time, a kind of stable-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and taking in account-- it's not that I was happy with what happened to Poland.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was really unhappy about this whole thing that they decided to divide the, the country, and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was against my grain.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But at any rate, as far as existence, it was a kind of a stable situation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I, I was kind of contented.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we lived-- the reason we lived with my in-laws, me and [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Zonya ?], was because they had the big apartment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the-- if, if we wouldn't stay there, the Russians would put in other people there, because they were not-- they were bringing a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they needed-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they needed space.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they did-- and they did terrible things, as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had-- in the same house at my-- in the-- at my in-laws, one room was occupied by a lawyer who came from-- was a refugee.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the, the Russians did announce that whoever, whoever wants to go back home should sign up that they wants to go back home, meaning going back to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if they don't want to, they had to say whether they want to stay or they want to go back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And whoever wrote that, they is going-- wants to go back, instead of sending them back, they took them to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They started the Soviet kind of, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] well, behavior.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
